# DevelopersHub Data Science & Analytics Internship

## Overview

This repository contains the tasks completed as part of the **DevelopersHub Data Science & Analytics Internship**. The projects demonstrate fundamental data science skills including data exploration, visualization, machine learning, and model evaluation using Python.

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn
- Jupyter Notebook

